###
### TESTS EDGE CASES
###

### TEST: Code EXPIRÉ (après 30 min)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/bookings/@bookingId/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer @passengerToken

{
  "code": "5847"
}

### Expected Error:
{
  "statusCode": 400,
  "message": "Le code de sécurité a expiré"
}

---

### TEST: Code INCORRECT
PATCH http://localhost:3000/bookings/@bookingId/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer @passengerToken

{
  "code": "9999"  ← MAUVAIS CODE
}

### Expected Error:
{
  "statusCode": 400,
  "message": "Code de sécurité invalide"
}

---

### TEST: Passager ne peut pas terminer trajet
PATCH http://localhost:3000/rides/@rideId/complete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer @passengerToken

### Expected Error:
{
  "statusCode": 403,
  "message": "Seul le chauffeur peut terminer ce trajet"
}

---

